      "description": "## What's changed   \r\n\r\n  ### Side panel — Dictionaries tab\r\n  - Lists all `.dict.json` files from the vault with name and entry count\r\n  - Import button — file picker, validates format, supports multi-select\r\n  - Remove button per file (sends to trash)\r\n\r\n  ### Bug fixes\r\n  - Removed `detachLeavesOfType` from `onunload` (Obsidian portal compliance)\r\n  - CSS `text-decoration-color` replaced with `border-bottom` (partial support warning)\r\n  - Regenerated `package-lock.json` (CI `concat-map` 404 fix)\r\n  - All Obsidian community portal warnings addressed\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/core-hn/pseudobsidian-ization/compare/0.1.0...0.1.1",
