      "description": "## What's changed\r\n\r\n  Compliance fixes for the Obsidian community plugin portal:\r\n  \r\n  - **License**: switched to GPL-3.0 (properly detected by GitHub)\r\n  - **minAppVersion**: bumped to 1.6.6 — enables use of `FileManager.trashFile()`\r\n    to respect the user's file deletion preference (trash vs. permanent delete)\r\n  - Replaced `builtin-modules` dependency with Node.js native `builtinModules`\r\n  - Added `@codemirror/view` and `@codemirror/state` to devDependencies\r\n  - Removed unused imports across UI files\r\n  - Explicit type casts on `JSON.parse` calls (no unsafe `any`)\r\n  - `window.setTimeout` and `activeDocument` for popout window compatibility\r\n  \r\n  **Full changelog:** v0.0.5 → v0.0.6\r\n",
