      "description": "## What's changed\r\n\r\n  Bug fixes and compliance improvements for the Obsidian community plugin portal:\r\n  \r\n  - Replaced `builtin-modules` dependency with Node.js native `builtinModules`\r\n  - Added `@codemirror/view` and `@codemirror/state` to devDependencies\r\n  - Removed unused imports across UI files\r\n  - Replaced `document` with `activeDocument` for popout window compatibility\r\n  - Replaced `setTimeout` with `window.setTimeout` for popout window compatibility\r\n  - Fixed explicit type casts on `JSON.parse` calls (`any` unsafe assignments)\r\n  - Updated `LICENSE` to CC BY 4.0 (GitHub-recognizable format)\r\n\r\n  **Full changelog:** v0.0.4 → v0.0.5",
